.TH FONT-PREVIEW 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "Font Preview Manual"
.SH NAME
font-preview - Font viewer with Unicode coverage analysis
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B font-preview
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBfont-preview\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita font viewer for Linux. It allows browsing all installed fonts via fontconfig, live text preview, side-by-side font comparison, Unicode and language coverage analysis, font metadata display, search and filter, and font favorites.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/font-preview/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/font-preview/
Cached data.
